These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, december, september
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, red, yellow, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person who likes red and the person who's birthday is in november##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | november    | december      | march      | september    |
| Color   | ebony | grey | red | yellow |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

