.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, thai, indian, australian
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, april, november
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the italian is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the thai##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the thai##1
7. the indian is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality          | italian     | australian     | thai       | indian    |
| Hobby         | photography | singing   | card-games | woodworking |
| Birthday   | november    | april | february    | september        |

