.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
House: craftsman, colonial, wooden, palace
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, hedgehog, dog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cycling, sailing
1. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
2. the colonial house is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
4. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
6. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| House      | craftsman | colonial  | wooden    | palace |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | dog  | lizard  | frog    |
| Sport         | climbing    | sailing | baseball | cycling  |

