.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, british, italian, german
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, sprite, tea
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person watching drama movies and the russian##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the italian##1
4. the italian is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking juice is the german##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the german is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality          | italian   | russian     | british | german |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| Beverage           | tea | sprite      | fanta     | juice       |

