.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
House: craftsman, palace, gothic-revival, wooden
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dressmaker, lawyer, librarian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, dahlia, tulip
1. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the palace house##3
3. the lawyer is the person who growslily##1
4. the architect is between the gothic-revival house and the palace house##2
5. the lawyer is on the right of the librarian##1
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the wooden house##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
8. the gothic-revival house is the person who growsdahlia##1
9. the palace house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| House          | gothic-revival      | wooden | palace      | craftsman |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | librarian | lawyer   |
| Flower   | dahlia    | tulip   | iris     | lily   |

