.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, sprite, iced-tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, june, august
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, biathlon, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Beverage           | cola    | coffee   | sprite | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | november     | june   | august         | december        |
| Sport         | biathlon | baseball | golf         | rowing       |

