.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, traveling, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, dannemann, chaman, tiparillo
There 4 different types of food: radish, pear, raspberry, orange
 1. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
 9. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
11. the dannemann-smoker is the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | traveling    | camping  | gardening | writing   |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | dannemann   | chaman    | pall-mall |
| Food   | orange      | raspberry | pear | radish  |

