.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, pop, gospel, d&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, ebony, red, aquamarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
8. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Music-Genre          | gospel | pop    | d&b | salsa    |
| Color         | red     | aquamarine | ebony  | azure |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

