.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, blues, folk, gospel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, lacrosse, cricket
1. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| Music-Genre           | trance    | gospel | folk     | blues |
| Sport   | handball | lacrosse    | volleyball | cricket    |

