.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, begonia, daffodil, tulip
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, milk, 7up, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, egyptian, mexican
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the chinese##3
4. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who growstulip##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the egyptian##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Flower          | begonia   | daffodil | rose | tulip |
| Beverage   | 7up   | milk     | juice      | soy-milk  |
| Nationality   | canadian | chinese   | egyptian    | mexican   |

