.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
House: townhouse, colonial, modern, farmhouse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, december, august
1. the lawyer is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
7. the modern house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person who's birthday is in june is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| House   | colonial             | townhouse     | farmhouse | modern  |
| Birthday         | november           | august | june   | december |

