3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the turkish is on the left or right of the teacher##3
5. the turkish is on the left or right of the teacher##3
6. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the russian##2
7. the turkish is the project-manager##1
8. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality    | turkish   | german   | russian    | egyptian |
| Job         | project-manager | teacher    | nurse      | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | mystery | superhero | satire   |

