.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, emerald, orange
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, scientific, time-travel, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, snowmobile, train
1. the person who likes apricot is the person driving the car##1
2. the person watching epic movies is between the person who likes lavender and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the train##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person who likes lavender is the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Color    | lavender      | apricot | orange       | emerald  |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel | epic | martial-arts    | scientific |
| Transport   | scooter     | car         | snowmobile | train     |

