.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, taxi, motorbike, quad-bike
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, fisherman, scientist, software-developer
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is the firefighter##1
3. the software-developer is on the far left or far right##3
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
5. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
7. the person driving the taxi is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Transport          | quad-bike          | motorbike     | boat   | taxi   |
| Job           | software-developer | firefighter | fisherman | scientist |
| Game   | chess          | billiard | scrabble   | backgammon |

