4. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growszinnia##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in august##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
