.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
City: berlin, liverpool, london, san-francisco
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, frog, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person traveling to berlin and the person traveling to london##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| City    | london | liverpool  | berlin  | san-francisco           |
| Pet     | lizard | frog | rat   | hamster |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 